fields.name: Michael Jackson
fields.description: An iconic and influential artist, whose extraordinary talent and dedication to music transformed the entertainment landscape, left an indelible mark on the world with his unique sound, style, and humanitarian efforts.

fields.name: Steve Jobs
fields.description: The visionary co-founder of Apple Inc. and a pioneer in the technology industry, profoundly changed the way we interact with technology. His innovative spirit and profound impact on computer, music, and mobile industries continue to inspire generations.
